title: 2020.05.09 - Cleaned the Olympia SM3

[[Saturday, May 09, 2020]]

I was waiting to get a new workbench before cleaning the [[Olympia SM3]] typewriter. It was a way to prod me to finally get a permanent tinkering station set up. Did that today. A little rubbing alcohol, a brush, and some patience and no more sticky keys.